                    <li>Marketing algorithms will also see a change. This will help airlines tailor messages to individual customers based on many factors. They are travel history, contextual variables, and the preference of the customers. </li>
                    <li>Airlines have to reduce their reliance on traditional technology providers, and instead, they must seek a hybrid approach. The following steps are kept in mind to capitalize on their growth in data science and analytics applications. </li>
                    <li>Ensuring that the data and advanced analytics capabilities are high on the agenda and prioritize investments and build a high-value program along with data strategy to support these initiatives. </li>
                </ul>

